/public/docs/attribute/IGNORE_RACE_SIZE

Format: (Living_Object)->set_attribute("IGNORE_RACE_SIZE", iValue);

Description:
  The IGNORE_RACE_SIZE will allow the Living_Object to
  ignore race size when wielding weapons. A small
  race would be able to dual wield 2 medium weapons
  for example. It won't allow them to wield 2 weapons
  that are normally restricted, like 2 LARGE, etc.
  The iValue is only used to turn the attribute
  on and off.
